{"title_page": "Plan Panni Pannanum", "text_new": "{{mi|{{Citation style|date=March 2020}}\n{{no footnotes|date=March 2020}}{{Notability|Films|date=April 2020}}\n}}\n'''''Plan Panni Pannanum''''' is an upcoming Indian Tamil-language Comedy film directedby Badri Venkatesh , produced by Rajesh Kumar &amp;amp; Sinthan L from Positive Print Studios. The story is written by G.Radhakrishnan, dialogues by A.C Karnamoorthy. The film stars Rio Raj and Ramya Nambessan playing the lead roles. The music for the film is composed by Yuvan Shankar Raja while Cinematography is handled by Rajasekar and editing is done by Sam.\n\n== Cast ==\n* [[Rio Raj]]\n* [[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]]\n* [[M. S. Bhaskar|M.S Bhaskar]]\n* [[Santhana Bharathi]]\n* [[Robo Shankar|Robo Sankar]]\n* [[Bala Saravanan]]\n* Thangadurai\n* [[Viji Chandrasekhar]]\n* Poornima Ravi\n\n== Music ==\nThe music and score is composed by [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]. The audio rights have been acquired by [[Sony Music India]]. The lyrics for the songs are written by [[Arunraja Kamaraj]] and Niranjan Bharathi.\n\nThe first single track, \"Ennodu Vaa\" was released on 27th February 2020. The song, was released live on [[Sun Music|sun music]] and was uploaded on [[YouTube (channel)|Youtube]] at the same time.\n\nThe audio launch happened on 11th March 2020 at [[Sathyam cinemas|Sathyam Cinemas]].\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|'''No.'''\n|'''Title'''\n|'''Lyrics'''\n|'''Singer(s)'''\n|-\n|1.\n|Plan Panni\n|[[Premgi Amaren]]\n|[[Arunraja Kamaraj]]\n|-\n|2.\n|Allola Kallolam\n|[[Remya Nambeesan|Ramya Nambessan]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|-\n|3.\n|Kanave Urave\n|[[Shreya Ghoshal]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|-\n|4.\n|Ennodu Vaa\n|[[Rajaganapathy|Raja Ganapathy]] , [[Ramya NSK]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|-\n|5.\n|Neengum Bothail\n|[[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]\n|Niranjan Bharathi\n|}\n\n== Promotion ==\nThe film's title was unveiled on 11 January 2020 which was released by [[Sivakarthikeyan]] and [[Vijay Sethupathi]]. The first look of the motion poster happened on 17 January 2020. The teaser was released on 21 February 2020 by [[Yuvan Shankar Raja]].\n\n== '''References''' ==\n{{No footnotes|date=April 2020}}\n{{Reflist}}\n* https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/movie-details/plan-panni-pannanum/movieshow/73225412.cms <span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span> \n* https://nettv4u.com/latest-tamil-celebrity-news/sivakarthikeyan-to-release-plan-panni-pannanum-first-look \n* https://www.behindwoods.com/tamil-movies-cinema-news-16/vijay-sethupathi-and-sivakarthikeyan-releases-rio-raj-remya-nambeesan-yuvan-s-plan-panni-pannanum-first-look-motion-poster.html<span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n* https://www.newsbugz.com/plan-panni-pannanum-tamil-movie/ \n* http://view7media.com/tag/plan-panni-pannanum-audio-launch/ \n* https://thandoratimes.com/gallery-Plan-Pani-Pannanum-Audio-Launch857-1<span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n* https://tamil.filmibeat.com/videos/i-said-only-one-joke-robo-shankar-plan-panni-pannanum-audio-launch-filmibeat-tamil-106660.html<span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n* https://www.cinemaexpress.com/stories/news/2020/jan/12/rio-rajs-film-with-badri-titled-plan-panni-pannanum-16494.html<span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n* https://www.cinemaexpress.com/stories/news/2020/jan/27/ramya-nambeesan-sings-for-yuvan-shankar-raja-in-plan-panni-pannanum-16724.html<span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n* https://tamil.indianexpress.com/lifestyle/rio-raj-plan-panni-pannanum-172846/<span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rio_Raj Rio Raj]</span>\n* https://www.behindwoods.com/tamil-movies-cinema-news-16/robo-shankar-trolls-vijay-tv-dd-and-thangadurai-in-the-press-meet-of-plan-panni-pannanum.html<span lang=\"EN-US\">[https://en.m.wikipedia.